# MAYA Architecture

Version: 1.1
Owner: Propify Brokerage Agency
Last updated: 2026-07-10

---

## Overview

MAYA is the AI Sales Executive of Propify Brokerage Agency.

Its mission is to communicate with real estate leads through WhatsApp, qualify them, answer project questions, send official project files, handle objections, and move qualified leads toward booking or purchasing.

This is Version 1 (MVP). The architecture is intentionally simple to allow fast deployment, fast testing, and continuous improvement.

---

## Core Components

### GitHub

GitHub is the permanent knowledge repository of MAYA.

It stores everything that defines how MAYA thinks and works:

- MAYA System Prompt
- Propify Sales Methodology
- Architecture Documentation
- AI Rules
- Business Rules
- Future Improvements
- Changelog

GitHub never stores project operational content such as brochures, price lists, images, or videos.

---

### Google Drive

Google Drive is MAYA's operational knowledge base.

Root folder: **Propify Property Intelligence**
(ID: 1h9bmeTizVD6tz--HcaNGEjaNAgQdWFsd)

Structure:

```
Propify Property Intelligence/
├── Projects/
│   └── [Developer] - [Project Name]/
│       ├── Project_Bible.md
│       ├── Sales_Playbook.md
│       └── Client_Files/
├── Database/
│   ├── Projects_Master  (Google Sheet — lightweight index of all market projects)
│   └── Project_Mapping  (Google Sheet — Project Code → Folder ID)
└── Raw_Data/
    ├── WhatsApp/
    └── Aqarmap/
```

**Standard project folder rule (no exceptions):**
Every project folder contains exactly:
- `Project_Bible.md` — strategic knowledge, read-only by MAYA, never sent to client
- `Sales_Playbook.md` — objection handling & qualification scripts, read-only, never sent to client
- `Client_Files/` — files approved for sharing with clients only

Google Drive is the single source of truth for all project content.

---

### n8n

n8n is the workflow and automation engine.

Responsibilities:

- Receive WhatsApp messages.
- Read Meta Click-to-WhatsApp referral (headline → Project Code).
- Detect the Entry Project via Project_Mapping sheet.
- Load the required project files from Google Drive.
- Build the AI context.
- Call OpenAI.
- Retrieve requested client files.
- Send WhatsApp reply.
- Save conversation history.

---

### OpenAI

OpenAI is the conversation engine.

Responsibilities:

- Understand customer messages.
- Follow the MAYA System Prompt.
- Use the Project Bible and Sales Playbook provided by n8n.
- Generate natural sales conversations.
- Qualify customers.
- Handle objections.
- Guide customers toward the next sales step.

OpenAI never becomes the source of truth. It only reasons over the context provided to it.

