## Three-Tier Knowledge Model

MAYA operates on three knowledge tiers during a conversation:

| Tier | Trigger | Action |
|---|---|---|
| **1. Entry Project** | Ad Project Code from Meta referral | Full Project_Bible + Sales_Playbook loaded. Stay here unless proven unsuitable. |
| **2. Pivot (Index)** | Customer asks about or hints at another project | Lightweight lookup in Projects_Master (name, developer, area, starting price only) |
| **3. Deep Dive** | Customer confirms serious interest in alternate project | Full Project_Bible + Sales_Playbook loaded for the new project |

This model keeps responses fast and accurate while allowing MAYA to serve the full market, not just one project.

